                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-192-off1086 t18180401-192-crimeloc1088"></join>, one watch, value 10l., one chain, value 4l., and two seals, value 2l., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18180401-192-victim1344" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Davidson
                     <interp inst="t18180401-192-victim1344" type="surname" value="Davidson"></interp>
